name: Swift Skip, The Shiatsu Squid
description:
Just a small arcade game demo, where you play a massaging squid trying to help his customers to relax. 

Made for Untitled Jam #41 in 42 Hours.

Design, Art and Music: DiCocco Theme: Relax

Sounds: DiCocco // www.zapsplat.com

Check the rule section ingame for any help. You can press 'F' to enable fullscreen mode.
